{"tid":1276822,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"市場社運 Market Social Movement","createTime":"2019-07-02T05:00:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-02T06:55:38.000Z","uid":93479,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"b0b7da5164db6d0812d2c03ae858eeb09ba7b855","tid":1276822,"uid":93479,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T05:00:57.000Z","msg":"市場經濟學，係透過供應需求，自動調節價格，達到 市場均衡 market equilibrium 。<br />\n<br />\n套用於今次社運，一邊和理非，一邊勇武，大家互相支持，互相調節，最後達成行動equilibrium 。承認有時好似一條蜈蚣，每隻腳都想自己行，但最後大家都會服從於市場大體，歸隊合作<br />\n<br />\n無辦法，抗爭無書睇，無Step by Step 跟，好似知想要乜，行去邊，但又唔知點做，卻又一定要行<br />\n<br />\n市場社運算是今次最合適的方法<br />\n<br />\n認同請給贊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b796def147e4996a2a82a6854e9b93fa2a64d28","tid":1276822,"uid":93479,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T06:09:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2861daeac89cbab6aa5d6e66b6b6f6c04c94f60c","tid":1276822,"uid":93479,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T06:55:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}